      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused A80 Supra Turbo featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant. This unit retains its factory sequential twin-turbocharger setup, delivering linear boost through the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains composed with a Torsen limited-slip differential ensuring optimal power delivery to the rear wheels. Mechanically sound with crisp shifts and a healthy compression profile, this vehicle has been maintained with an emphasis on drivetrain longevity. Recent service includes a timing belt refresh and cooling system overhaul, making it a turnkey performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
